st `publish_agentcube_workflow` integration\n610:   - AgentCube provider creates AgentRuntime CR\n611:   - Verify CR spec matches metadata\n612:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_integration.py`\n613:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_integration.py::TestPublishIntegration::test_publish_agentcube_workflow -v`\n614: \n615: - [ ] **T12.4**: Test `publish_k8s_workflow` integration\n616:   - K8s provider creates Deployment + Service\n617:   - Verify deployment ready, service accessible\n618:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_integration.py`\n619:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_integration.py::TestPublishIntegration::test_publish_k8s_workflow -v`\n620: \n621: - [ ] **T12.5**: Test `error_recovery_metadata` integration\n622:   - Deployment fails, metadata records error\n623:   - Retry succeeds, metadata updated\n624:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_integration.py`\n625:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_integration.py::TestPublishIntegration::test_error_recovery -v`\n626: \n627: ### Phase 13: Dependencies & Validation (ST-13)\n628: \n629: - [ ] **T13.1**: Add `kubernetes` dependency to `pyproject.toml`\n630:   - Version: `kubernetes>=28.0.0`\n631:   - Add to `[project.optional-dependencies]` as `k8s` extras\n632:   - File: `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml`\n633:   - Verification: `pip install kubernetes && python -c \"import kubernetes\"`\n634: \n635: - [ ] **T13.2**: Update `services/__init__.py` exports\n636:   - Add `KubernetesProvider`, `AgentCubeProvider` to exports\n637:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n638:   - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.services import KubernetesProvider, AgentCubeProvider\"`\n639: \n640: - [ ] **T13.3**: Update `runtime/__init__.py` exports\n641:   - Add `PublishRuntime` to exports\n642:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n643:   - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.runtime import PublishRuntime\"`\n644: \n645: - [ ] **T13.4**: